name: Ferne
description: There once was a family of fairies who lived in a cottage of trees. The fairies were somewhat peculiar, and came in a set of three. The sisters Faye, Ferne, and Fawn noticed one day their tree was gone. They moved to a new one not far away, and a set of three they decided to stay. This one is Ferne's home, set in the tree's hollow, a cozy place for her this year, and hopefully many to follow
